law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 491, effective January 2, 1978. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2920, 3154, 3529.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Fees of witnesses in police courts, cities of first, second and fourth classes.
